	  instead of File.open(...).read. [ruby-dev:21964]

	* test/wsdl/emptycomplextype.wsdl, test/wsdl/test_emptycomplextype.rb:
	  simplify the test case.

	* test/wsdl/axisArray/*: add tests for axis's array encoding.

