	* test/ruby/test_beginendblock.rb: add tests for nested BEGIN/END.

	* test/ruby/beginmainend.rb: add tests for nested BEGIN/END.

	* test/ruby/endblockwarn.rb: new file added to test of END-in-method
	  warning.

